}}
PRIORITAS: decision_rule > failure_mode > procedural > causal > heuristic
HASILKAN MINIMAL 7 NODE untuk topik ini.
HANYA OUTPUT JSON ARRAY. JANGAN MARKDOWN, JANGAN KOMENTAR."""
    response = await ai(system_prompt)
    clean_response = re.sub(r'```json\s*|\s*```$', '', response).strip()
    try:
        new_nodes = json.loads(clean_response)
        if not isinstance(new_nodes, list):
            new_nodes = [new_nodes]
        validated_nodes = []
        for node in new_nodes:
            if "id" in node and "statement" in node:
